decks.notes: The main focus of this deck is to control the game through counterspells and disruption while setting up for a powerful combo finish with cards like High Tide and Brain Freeze. The deck aims to stall the opponent's strategy with a variety of counter spells like Force of Will and Counterspell, before going off with a big mana turn using High Tide and Turnabout to generate a massive amount of mana. Once the combo pieces are assembled, the deck can cast Brain Freeze to mill out the opponent's library and win the game. The deck is designed to be fast and efficient, using card draw and filtering spells like Brainstorm and Serum Visions to find the combo pieces quickly.
